# Ask any silly question on statistics
# Scheme; the question is a record (starting with ":")
# 5 items in a record
# 1 item is the question
# 2,3,4,5 items are answer
# the good item is the item marked with a ""
# the answers will be shuffled

:What is an average?;
The half of the sum;
The sum of all answers divided by 2;
The total of a numbers set  divided by the sum; 
The total of a numbers set  divided by the amount of numbers

:What is a median of a numbers set?;
the median is the number with the highest frequency of a sorted set;
the median is the number with the lowest frequency of a sorted set;
the median is the number with the average frequency of a sorted set;
the median is the number in the middle of a sorted set

:What is a median?;
the middle of the first quartilerange;
the third quartile;
the first quartile;
the second quartile

:What is a weight average of a numbers set?;
the total of all numbers divided by its weight;
the total of all numbers divided by the total weight;
the multiplication of all weights divided by the sum of the numbers;
the sum of the numbers each multiplied with its own weight divide by the total weight

