:The sum of  N  numbers is  S  with which formula can you calculate the average?;
(S+N)/S;
(N*S)/N;
N/S;
S/N

:We have the numbers N1 N2 N3    with their corresponding weights  W1 W2 W3  Which of these formulas represents the total sum of these numbers?;
(N1+N2+N3)*(W1+W2+W3);
(N1/W1)+(N2/W2)+(N3/W3);
(N1+W1)+(N2+W2)+(N3+W3);
(N1*W1)+(N2*W2)+(N3*W3)

:We have the numbers N1 N2 N3    with their corresponding weights  W1 W2 W3  Which of these formulas represents the average of these numbers?;
(N1+N2+N3)*(W1+W2+W3)/3;
(N1 + W1 + N2 + W2 + N3 + W3)/(W1+W2+W3);
(N1*W1 + N2*W2 + N3*W3)/3;
(N1*W1 + N2*W2 + N3*W3)/(W1+W2+W3)

